pump.io version 0.01
====================

This is a module that provides a simple object oriented interface to the
pump.io social networking software.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

LWP

